regularly analyze product performance and communicate best practice for enhancing performance to relevant stakeholder increase data access through the construction of dashboard and repeated report to ensure primary data source are accessible accurate and meet the need of our internal stakeholder
templatize and standardize repeated analysis
take ownership of assigned project and serve a a central point of contact between the research team the tech team business team and other internal stakeholder
monitor data accuracy and raise issue to relevant stakeholder
